analysis: The agent incorrectly capitalized the values for "investmentSize" and "marketDynamics" in the function arguments, leading to a mismatch with the expected parameter values and causing the evaluator to not recognize the function call as correct.
The agent used "Detailed" for the outputDetail parameter instead of the required "Summary", leading to a parameter mismatch and no matching function call by the evaluator.
The agent used "Comprehensive" instead of the required "Detailed" value for the "detailLevel" parameter, causing a mismatch with the expected function call arguments.

The agent incorrectly added an unsupported "weatherDetail" parameter to the FlightStatus_checkFlightAndWeather function call, causing the call signature to mismatch the tool schema and resulting in evaluation failure.

The agent incorrectly used a numeric value ("8.0") for the "ratingThreshold" parameter instead of the expected categorical value ("good"), resulting in a parameter mismatch and failure to match the required function call.
The agent incorrectly formatted the timezone parameter as "Eastern Standard Time (EST)" instead of the expected "EST", leading to a mismatch with the required function call signature.
